title: New poll suggests a resurgent Clinton has caught up to Sanders in New Hampshire
text: Hillary Rodham Clinton has caught up to Bernie Sanders in the key early-voting state of New Hampshire, a poll released Wednesday shows. The WBUR survey giving Clinton a four-point lead is the latest to record an upswing for Clinton following last week’s Democratic debate. Her New Hampshire lead is within the poll’s margin of […] ...
